{"tid":352073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]四川九寨溝七級地震","createTime":"2017-08-08T13:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T14:49:44.000Z","uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29f66f13257617ed0bc70ad8f83d12c59782624d","tid":352073,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:56:42.000Z","msg":"中國地震台網指出，今晚9時19分在四川阿壩州九寨溝縣附近，發生7級左右地震，震源深度20公里。在四川成都、陝西西安、甘肅蘭州都有民眾聲稱感到震動。<br />\n<br />\n有身處九寨溝的民眾稱地震發生後當地全縣停電、建築物牆身剝落，中國移動的信號消失，大批民眾已湧到室外暫避。"},{"pid":"d16d1da9d7886cee1045de9ce35e79eba733fc41","tid":352073,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05d82c94030a3523d90407b49c2ff7ea60dba81","tid":352073,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170808&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57057775 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170808%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57057775%20&d=%2BvpOqeBWzixi1gP9YfE2gbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e272b0cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170808%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57057775%20&h=e29641d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170808&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57057775 </a>川九寨溝發生7級地震 縣城停電建築物損毀"},{"pid":"3fb38ea97993ab5c8785b3c2f69d9f73d7637d34","tid":352073,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:57:54.000Z","msg":"又被捐錢"},{"pid":"d075ded76992ee56da7489401193331e88488aef","tid":352073,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"726b1bffda918a8d2757b0f779070dd2903c8ea1","tid":352073